Data Abundance
In last 30 years the data generated by computing devices, sensors and software has increased exponentially. There is a need to develop new platforms and strategies to store, interpret, transform, aggregate, visualize and consume data.
Data is generated and consumed by businesses and general public, using applications and computing platforms.
GDPR - General Data Protection Regulation
PCI DSS - Payment Cart Industry Data Security Standard

Data can be structured, unstructured or aggregated.

Azure provides comprehensive set of data technologies to its users. It keeps on adding new technologies as and when they are available. This enables users to explore new technologies in preview mode and they pay for only what they use and for the time they use it.
